                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.458/10–1049: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Truman</persName> to Acting
                        President <persName type="to">Li Tsung-jen</persName> of China</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-10-10T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >October 10, 1949—5 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>On this national anniversary I extend to Your Excellency and to the people of
                    China the sincere good wishes of the people of the United States.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Harry</hi> S. <hi rend="smallcaps">Truman</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
